      <title>欧洲股票在五年内随着特朗普关税缓刑而跳高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）停止计划对数十个贸易伙伴实施更高互惠关税的计划之后，欧洲股票集会，缓解了对全球贸易战的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 00:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
